:::The Protectrons:::

::The small space shuttle Master cruises through transwarp space.  As it gets 
near Prehistoric earth, Chromedome looks to his crew::
Chromedome: Alright, men, you remember our mission.
Brainstorm: Yep, the Maximal Elders sent us to earth to aid the Maximals in 
battle with some faction called the Alliance.
Highbrow: They sound like tough customers.
Hardhead: Tough customers? Hah! We'll dispatch them easily!
Chromedome: Dont be cocky Hardhead, we have reports of a strong army 
terrorizing the CF, a great battle cruiser.  For all we know the Alliance 
might be the dominant faction on this planet.
Brainstorm: Chromedome, my scanners detect a spare asteroid headed for the 
ship.
Chromedome: Well, cant you just-
::The asteroid hit, an explosian shattering the Master, sending it plummeting 
towards earth::

--part1_a2.e60992c.2787ff2f_boundary
